            </a>
    
</div>				<div class="partage">
    <div class="shared-counts-wrap shortcode style-icon"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://esse.ca/intimation-culturelle-regime-appropriationniste-et-arts-visuels/&amp;display=popup&amp;ref=plugin&amp;src=share_button" title="Share on Facebook"  target="_blank"  rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"  class="shared-counts-button facebook shared-counts-no-count" data-postid="146376" data-social-network="Facebook" data-social-action="Share" data-social-target="https://esse.ca/intimation-culturelle-regime-appropriationniste-et-arts-visuels/"><span class="shared-counts-icon-label"><span class="shared-counts-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18.8125" height="32" viewBox="0 0 602 1024"><path d="M548 6.857v150.857h-89.714q-49.143 0-66.286 20.571t-17.143 61.714v108h167.429l-22.286 169.143h-145.143v433.714h-174.857v-433.714h-145.714v-169.143h145.714v-124.571q0-106.286 59.429-164.857t158.286-58.571q84 0 130.286 6.857z"></path></svg></span><span class="shared-counts-label">Facebook</span></span></a><a href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://esse.ca/intimation-culturelle-regime-appropriationniste-et-arts-visuels/&amp;text=Intimation%20culturelle%2C%20r%C3%A9gime%20appropriationniste%20et%20arts%20visuels" title="Share on Twitter"  target="_blank"  rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"  class="shared-counts-button twitter shared-counts-no-count" data-postid="146376" data-social-network="Twitter" data-social-action="Tweet" data-social-target="https://esse.ca/intimation-culturelle-regime-appropriationniste-et-arts-visuels/"><span class="shared-counts-icon-label"><span class="shared-counts-icon"><svg version="1.1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="29.71875" height="32" viewBox="0 0 951 1024"><path d="M925.714 233.143q-38.286 56-92.571 95.429 0.571 8 0.571 24 0 74.286-21.714 148.286t-66 142-105.429 120.286-147.429 83.429-184.571 31.143q-154.857 0-283.429-82.857 20 2.286 44.571 2.286 128.571 0 229.143-78.857-60-1.143-1